**Missing headers include:**
| Header | Risk if absent |
|---|---|
| `X-Content-Type-Options` | MIME-type sniffing attacks |
| `X-Frame-Options` / `CSP frame-ancestors` | Clickjacking |
| `Strict-Transport-Security` | Protocol downgrade / MITM |
| `Content-Security-Policy` | XSS, data injection |
| `Referrer-Policy` | Information leakage via Referer |
| `X-Powered-By: Express` | Technology fingerprinting (auto-added by Express) |

**Fix — add `helmet`:**

```bash
